![Episode106.jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1578271568625-NZJSZMM27KITQPWN2RKO/Episode106.jpg)

Merry Cliquemas one and all! Ring in the holiday with a Major Issues tradition, the return of WHICH WAS WORSE! In this episode, we try to decide DEFINITIVELY which was the worst Comic Book Christmas Movie when we defend and assault Iron Man 3 and Batman Returns. We pit both movies against one another, bringing out their strengths and shining a light on their weaknesses, all this knock down drag out episode of The Major Issues Podcast!

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
Send us feedback at **ComicBookClique@Gmail.com!** You Are Worthy! 

